OL,3,CIsle of Man becomes first parliament
OL,4,Cin British Isles to pass assisted dying
OL,6,FTerminally ill people on the Isle of
OL,7,FMan will be given "autonomy and
OL,8,Fchoice" at the end of their lives as
OL,9,Fthe island becomes the first part of
OL,10,Fthe British Isles to pass assisted
OL,11,Fdying legislation.
OL,13,FDr Alex Allinson who introduced the
OL,14,Fprivate member's bill in 2022, said he
OL,15,Fhad "met many patients who have wanted
OL,16,Fthis option" and described it as a
OL,17,Fprivilege to have been able to bring
OL,18,Fthe Bill forward.
