OL,3,CIsle of Man becomes first parliament
OL,4,Cin British Isles to pass assisted dying
OL,6,FThe proposed legislation was voted
OL,7,Fthrough by the parliament's upper
OL,8,Fchamber, known as the Legislative
OL,9,FCouncil, meaning the Bill will now be
OL,10,Fput forward for royal assent, at which
OL,11,Fpoint it will become law.
OL,13,FDr Allinson, a member of the House of
OL,14,FKeys (MHK), said he is now hopeful it
OL,15,Fcan become law later this year, with
OL,16,Fan assisted dying service in place by
OL,17,F2027.
