OL,3,CIsle of Man becomes first parliament
OL,4,Cin British Isles to pass assisted dying
OL,6,F"It has been a long process, but it
OL,7,Fwas something that, when I went into
OL,8,Fpolitics, I was committed to try to
OL,9,Fadvance," he said.
OL,11,F"I'm very grateful to be in the
OL,12,Fprivileged position of being able to
OL,13,Fbring this legislation through. People
OL,14,Fhave been trying on the Isle of Man
OL,15,Ffor the last 20 years to provide
OL,16,Fdignity and autonomy for those who are
OL,17,Ffacing an imminent death.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
