OL,3,CIsle of Man becomes first parliament
OL,4,Cin British Isles to pass assisted dying
OL,6,F"And I see this as a culmination of
OL,7,Fthe efforts of many members of our
OL,8,Fcommunity to provide for assisted
OL,9,Fdying for people on the Isle of Man."
OL,11,FAs it stands, the Isle of Man Bill is
OL,12,Fonly for adults resident on the island
OL,13,Ffor five years who have a terminal
OL,14,Fillness with a life expectancy of no
OL,15,Fmore than 12 months, and who have a
OL,16,Fsettled intention to end their life.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@eO]
