OL,3,CIsle of Man becomes first parliament
OL,4,Cin British Isles to pass assisted dying
OL,6,FBut Dr Allinson said while he
OL,7,Funderstands and respects the
OL,8,Fviewpoints of those opposed to
OL,9,Flegalisation, the Bill had been
OL,10,Fdrafted through "a very careful
OL,11,Fprocess", with expert evidence taken
OL,12,Finto account throughout.
OL,14,FHe added that the implementation of
OL,15,Fthe law "will involve more
OL,16,Fconsultation, more guidelines, more
OL,17,Fsafeguards and more parliamentary
OL,18,Fdebates in terms of the underlying
OL,19,Fregulations and secondary legislation".
