OL,3,CIsle of Man becomes first parliament
OL,4,Cin British Isles to pass assisted dying
OL,6,F"This is legislation probably that
OL,7,Fwill only be used by a very small
OL,8,Fnumber of people but for those people
OL,9,Fit's a very important step forward, in
OL,10,Fterms of autonomy and choice at the
OL,11,Fend of your life," he said.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, a committee of MPs at
OL,14,FWestminster are nearing the end of
OL,15,Ftheir scrutiny of a Bill to legalise
OL,16,Fassisted dying in England and Wales.
